{"tid":690378,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國對外國晶片生產商發起調查 意圖施壓奪取技術？","createTime":"2018-06-04T22:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T01:43:01.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"07570ee2d7ef8805c952e450bdb025b34f188245","tid":690378,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T22:20:28.000Z","msg":"中國對外國晶片生產商發起調查<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/china/article/1858301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F1858301&d=AFj9vG7%2FTfa%2BdsO23fMBp4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=4b64b291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/china/article/1858301</a><br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報道，中國監管機構正調查存儲晶片生產商美光科技(Micron Technology)、三星電子和海力士半導體(SK Hynix)，這三家公司均表示，國家市場監督管理總局官員近期走訪了其中國辦公室。<br />\n<br />\n國家市場監管總局暫未對此作出置評。<br />\n<br />\n上述三家公司是DRAM晶片的主要供應商。三家公司稱，正在配合調查，但未透露調查內容。<br />\n<br />\n分析人士表示，調查可能涉及中國智能手機生產商正面臨的DRAM晶片價格上升因素，因為需求持續超過供應。<br />\n<br />\nMarco Rubio<br />\nMarco Rubio<br />\n@marcorubio<br />\n&middot;<br />\n3h<br />\n#China now undertaking a blatant effort to use a pric&shy;ing &ldquo;in&shy;ves&shy;ti&shy;ga&shy;tion&rdquo; to harass &amp; pressure chip mak&shy;ers, including a U.S. company, to transfer technology to them. We should always remember that China plays hardball, we must as well.  <br />\n<br />\nChina Launches Probe of Foreign Chip Makers<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/china-launches-probe-of-foreign-chip-makers-1528098432\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fchina-launches-probe-of-foreign-chip-makers-1528098432&d=AFj9vG7%2FTfa%2BdsO23fMBp4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=7d56f569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/china-launches-probe-of-foreign-chip-makers-1528098432</a><br />\n<br />\nBEIJING&mdash;Chinese regulators are investigating memory-chip makers Micron Technology Inc., Samsung Electronics Co. and SK Hynix Inc., all three of which said their China offices have received visits recently."},{"pid":"d52d973fa9c6a82b1f76ad03d85cb95ca55334d6","tid":690378,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T22:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac14cd228b5589bad00cc63d6531f34a7ce2f2e","tid":690378,"uid":47259,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T23:22:20.000Z","msg":"支那自己DRAM 0良率唔怪自己走去屈人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f2f1560f7c4e2795ab0fb2574af0e54845402e","tid":690378,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T03:39:59.000Z","msg":"全部停止供貨3個月啦"},{"pid":"c7a7aa1a3aee7b407525c43db399dc54d8750d6c","tid":690378,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdbd1e3f9747f119e3c0278b20eeb31d57b77c3","tid":690378,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:39:12.000Z","msg":"自取滅亡"},{"pid":"3812864e7cc1074e0e0230f089ae460427475f85","tid":690378,"uid":44171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T05:43:21.000Z","msg":"唔賣去支那好過啦, 幾多年先賺得返80億美金 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5003e52bf371738a43065dc53a30cba795adeb65","tid":690378,"uid":83623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3ac14cd228b5589bad00cc63d6531f34a7ce2f2e","tid":690378,"uid":47259,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1